description:
This is a 14 minute workout called '15 MIN Guided Meditation For Manifestation & Success | Feed Your Truth & Inner Fire' from the channel Boho Beautiful Yoga.
The workout falls under Rest/Meditation.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow and The Deep Recharge vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: This quick and effective 15 minute guided meditation will help you manifest success as you train and master your mind to stay focussed and calm. In uncertain times such as these, through a consistent meditation practice you can take back control of your life by finding conscious stillness to reconnect to your truth and inner fire.
